    {
        "url": "/quotes/per_petterson_685662",
        "quote": "There is always this quarrel about what is preferable: the straight, naturalistic, epic storytelling or the modernistic, disjointed, slightly hermetic one. To me it does not matter, as long as it's good. I like both kinds. Although the common reader seems to prefer the first, which is to be expected, and who would blame her?",
        "author": {
            "name": "Per Petterson",
            "url": "/quotes/per_petterson_685662"
