    {
        "url": "/quotes/per_petterson_685638",
        "quote": "I was born in 1952, so obviously the sixties were important. That's when I came of age. It was also a revolutionary period, a complete break with the generation before us in terms of culture, literature, music, and in politics, of course. 1968 was an important year; I was 16, and the world became clear to me, visible, so to say.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Per Petterson",
            "url": "/quotes/per_petterson_685638"
